| CONT_EVENT_INST_ITEM_ID | CONTRACT_EVENT_INSTANCE_ID | LAST_UPDATED_DATE | CREATION_DATE | CONT_EVNT_INST_ITM_REF_TYPE_ID | CREATED_BY | GL_PRODUCT_GROUP | LAST_UPDATED_BY | DW_CREATION_DATE | LAST_UPDATED | CONT_EVNT_INST_ITM_REF_ID | QUANTITY | DW_LAST_UPDATED | DW_DEDUP_COL |
